{"article_id":"f6Vu8M26mP9mkgBu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"US President Donald Trump announced Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that three Americans","depth":12},{"id":3,"text":"held in North Korea","depth":12},{"id":4,"text":"have been released","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and are on their way back home .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"`` I am pleased to inform you","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"that Secretary of State Mike Pompeo is in the air and on his way back from North Korea with the 3 wonderful gentlemen","depth":13},{"id":8,"text":"that everyone is looking so forward to meeting .","depth":13},{"id":9,"text":"They seem to be in good health , ''","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"The Americans","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"-- Kim Dong Chul , Kim Hak-song and Kim Sang Duk ,","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"also known as Tony Kim --","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"were freed","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"while Pompeo was on a visit to the North Korean capital of Pyongyang","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to discuss President Trump 's upcoming summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Pompeo and his `` guests '' will be arriving at Joint Base Andrews in Maryland at 2 a.m . ET , presumably Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"where he will greet them .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"I am pleased to inform you","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that Secretary of State Mike Pompeo is in the air and on his way back from North Korea with the 3 wonderful gentlemen","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"that everyone is looking so forward to meeting .","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"They seem to be in good health .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Also , good meeting with Kim Jong Un .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Date & Place set .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"`` We would like to express our deep appreciation to the United States government , President Trump , Secretary Pompeo , and the people of the United States","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"for bringing us home , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"the trio said in the statement","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"which the State Department supplied to journalists","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"traveling with Pompeo .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Kim Dong Chul has been in North Korean custody since late 2015 ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"but the other two detainees were arrested last spring , after Trump 's inauguration","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"as tensions between Washington and Pyongyang were beginning to ramp up .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"The White House has often brought up their cases","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"when discussing North Korea issues .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"As both sides began laying the groundwork for the Trump and Kim 's meeting","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"-- which would be the first-ever between a sitting US President and North Korean leader --","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"the Trump administration made it clear","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that releasing the three Americans would be viewed as a gesture of good will .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"In this Wednesday , photo","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"provided on Thursday by the North Korean government ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo shakes hands with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Aboard the plane","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"leaving North Korea ,","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"he was `` thrilled to have them back . ''","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Pompeo told the small contingent of reporters","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"traveling with him","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"that the detainees appear to be in good health ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"or at least as healthy","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"as can be","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"considering the circumstances","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"surrounding their detention .","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"`` I had productive meetings in Pyongyang with Chairman","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"( Kim Jong Un )","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"and made progress .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"I 'm delighted to bring home three Americans , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"he said on Twitter .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"I had productive meetings in Pyongyang with Chairman Kim Jong-un","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"and made progress .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"I 'm delighted to bring home three Americans .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"- Secretary Pompeo","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"( @ SecPompeo )","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"May 9 , 2018","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"Both Trump and Pompeo said","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"the meetings with Kim went well","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"-- the President called it a `` good meeting '' in a tweet --","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and confirmed","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that a date and location for the summit has been set ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"echoing a similar comments","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"made Tuesday at the White House .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"The state-run Korea Central News Agency said","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that Kim decided to release the Americans at Trump 's suggestion .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"It added","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that Pompeo and Kim `` reached a satisfactory consensus on the issues","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"discussed ''","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"and described the talks as `` very beneficial . ''","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` We 're honored by the fact","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"that the three gentlemen are coming home","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"and I look forward to seeing you , ''","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"Trump said during a Cabinet meeting on Wednesday .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Secretary Pompeo and his `` guests '' will be landing at Andrews Air Force Base at 2:00 A.M. in the morning .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"I will be there","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"to greet them .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"Very exciting !","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"May 9 , 2018","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"A statement","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"released by the White House","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Trump `` appreciates Kim Jong Un 's action","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"to release these American citizens","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"and views this as a gesture of goodwill . ''","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"`` The three Americans appear to be in good condition","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"and were all able to walk on the plane","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"without assistance .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"All Americans look forward to welcoming them home","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and to seeing them reunited with their loved ones , ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"the statement said .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"The family of Tony Kim specifically thanked Trump","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"for working to secure the Americans ' release .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"`` We are very grateful for the release of our husband and father , Tony Kim , and the other two American detainees .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"We want to thank all of those","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"who have worked toward and contributed to his return home .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"We also want to thank the President","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"for engaging directly with North Korea .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Mostly , we thank God for Tony 's safe return , ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"the family wrote in a statement Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"`` We appreciate all of the support and prayers of friends and even strangers during this challenging year .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"You are dear to our hearts .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"We ask","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that you continue to pray for the people of North Korea","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and for the release of all","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"who are still being held .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Thank you , ''","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"it added .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Tony Kim and Kim Hak-song ,","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"who were arrested in April and May of 2017 , respectively ,","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"were both accused of carrying out `` hostile acts '' against the Kim Jong Un regime .","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"Both worked at the Pyongyang University of Science and Technology ,","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"which bills itself as the only privately run university in the North Korean capital .","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"Joseph Yun ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"who until March was the administration 's top diplomat","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"working on North Korea issues ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"told CNN","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"the release of the three Americans is `` terrific news ''","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"and he hopes","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"they `` are in good health . '' `` I 'm delighted for their families ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"as you know","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"I 've met all three of them last year","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"when I was there ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"so I could n't be more delighted , ''","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"now the US must close this chapter","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"and move on with summit preps .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"`` What happens to denuclearization , what happens to peace treaty ...","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"those are the key issues","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"we need to concentrate ( on ) , ''","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"said Yun ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"who is now a CNN global affairs analyst .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"An official with knowledge of the negotiations previously told CNN","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"that the North Koreans decided to free the Americans two months ago ,","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"and that North Korea 's foreign minister , Ri Yong Ho , had proposed their release during his visit to Sweden in March","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"At the time , US officials insisted","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"that their release `` must not be related or used","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"to loosen the main issue of denuclearization , ''","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"the source said ,","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"but that message seems to have changed in recent days ,","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"according to a source at the National Security Council ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"the development would be viewed as a goodwill gesture ahead of the planned summit with Kim Jong Un .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"Trump and his allies outside the government had sought to fan the heightened expectations ahead of Wednesday 's announcement ,","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"casting the potential development as evidence of his negotiating prowess ahead of the summit .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"Trump had hinted at a potential development in their case last week in a tweet :","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"`` As everybody is aware ,","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"the past Administration has long been asking for three detainees to be released from a North Korean Labor camp ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"but to no avail .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"Stay tuned ! ''","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"He did not mention","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"that two of the Americans had been detained","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"after he became President .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"And Rudy Giuliani , a member of Trump 's legal team but not himself an employee of the government , teased the release last week as well .","depth":5},{"id":165,"text":"CLARIFICATION :","depth":5},{"id":166,"text":"This story has been updated near the end of the story","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"to reflect","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"that the announcement was made on Wednesday .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":337,"left":0,"right":336,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":336,"left":290,"right":335,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":285,"right":289,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":268,"right":284,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":203,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":198,"right":202,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":184,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":173,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":1,"right":172,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":171,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":170,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":177,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":176,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":175,"right":9,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":6,"right":174,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":174,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":11,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"ela